      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "ども",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for your hard work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.699999976158142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うおおおおっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wooaah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.833333309491475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 3.8333333094914783
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "LizNoirサイコー！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir is the best!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.233333285649618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 9.18333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――三枝の突然の退社という危機を乗り越えて、莉央と葵は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Having overcome the crisis of Saegusa’s sudden resignation‚ Rio and Aoi",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.183333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 12.95
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "順調にトップアイドルの階段を駆け上がっていた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…were steadily climbing the stairs to becoming top idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.966666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7150,
          "startTime": 20.116666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 16.250000000000004
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――次回のNEXT VENUSグランプリの優勝候補筆頭",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――There were even voices saying that they were",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.250000000000004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "との声も上がっていた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…the top candidates to win the next NEXT VENUS Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.91587986817231,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2534.120131827688,
          "startTime": 22.45
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 22.35000000000001
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 22.35000000000001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "おめでとう、東京レイーズをこんなに早く",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Congratulations. You’re the first to sell out",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.75,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "満員にしたのは貴方達が初めてよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tokyo Rays so quickly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.85000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――控え室に戻った二人を待っていたのは姫野霧子",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Waiting for the two as they returned to the dressing room",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.38442383747476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "現在のLizNoirのプロデューサーだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…was Kiriko Himeno‚ LizNoir’s current producer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.61775717080809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "きっと明日のスポーツ紙に載るわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’ll surely be in tomorrow’s sports newspapers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.45109050414142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "テレビ局からの取材依頼も来てるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve also gotten interview requests from TV stations.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.28442383747476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 41.551090504141385
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ほ、本当ですか！？\nやったわね、葵",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Really!?\nWe did it‚ Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.05109050414143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 45.85109050414139
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、僕マスコミは苦手なんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ I’m not good with the media‚ though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.851090504141425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 49.63533074996048
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "取材には莉央が中心で答えてちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio‚ you handle the interview.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.63533074996052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "葵はそばで頷いていればいいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi‚ just nod along beside her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.001997416627184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 55.535330749960515
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "うん、それがいい\n頼むよ、莉央",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ that sounds good.\nI'm counting on you‚ Rio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.901997416627175,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2886.977647599686,
          "startTime": 58.4223083975602
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "僕が話すとなんだか微妙な空気になるんだよね\nどうしてかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The atmosphere always gets kinda awkward when I talk.\nI wonder why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.12230839756023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 63.855641730893566
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "そうやって思い付きで喋っているからよ……\nまあ諦めてるけどね……あら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s because you say whatever comes to mind…\n…Well‚ I’ve given up…huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.72230839756023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 69.42230839756022
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――莉央の視線が葵の持っているスマホの画面で止まる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Rio’s gaze stops on the screen of Aoi’s smartphone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.91901250473258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "見知らぬアイドルらしき少女のライブ動画",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a live video of a girl who seems to be an unfamiliar idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.41901250473258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 77.2856791713992
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "葵、その子……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi‚ that girl…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.28567917139922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 79.22032768519317
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、莉央も気付いた？\nすごいよ、この子",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ you noticed too‚ Rio?\nShe’s amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.1536610185265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 82.72032768519317
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――葵の隣に立ち、一緒に食い入るように動画を観る",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――She stands next to Aoi and they watch the video intently together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.72032768519317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "小さなライブハウスでパフォーマンスを披露する少女",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A girl is performing at a small live house.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.08699435185984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――葵よりも自由で、莉央よりも力強く、二人の良い所を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Her dancing and singing is freer than Aoi’s‚ more powerful than Rio’s‚ and it’s as if she’s taken",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.6536610185265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "合わせて、さらにブーストをかけたような踊りと歌",
      "translations": {
        "en": "the best parts of both of them and boosted it even further.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.28699435185985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 96.72032768519321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "……誰なの、この子……\nこんな子、知らないわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Who is she…?\nI don’t know her…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2203276851932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 100.78699435185986
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、才能も技術も間違いなくトップクラスだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But her talent and technique are definitely top-class.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.78699435185986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 105.35366101852652
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "長瀬麻奈よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana Nagase.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.35366101852652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
